{"tw": {"2954880": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "VR女友 / VR-Kanojo", "steam_appid": 2954880, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 零距離戀愛，即刻展開 -</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《VR女友》製作人傾力打造的全新作品──更有趣、更可愛！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在次世代 VR 戀愛模擬器 <strong>《VR女友》</strong>中，與女主角夕陽櫻在「幾乎鼻尖相觸」的距離甜蜜相伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即時全光源照明與全新著色器重現肌膚的透亮感與眼眸的光澤，戴上 VR 頭戴式顯示器，前所未有的臨場感瞬間包圍你。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >零距離真實感</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算近到鼻尖相碰也不失真，櫻輕聲呼吸的氣息都讓人沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/b117e39a5043d7a688c374163ff35cd0.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/b117e39a5043d7a688c374163ff35cd0.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戀人般親密互動</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整理書架時將櫻摟入懷中、浴室溫柔洗身、心跳加速的親吻——借助「觀看·觸碰」直觀操作盡情撒嬌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.mp4?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富的場景與服裝</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >客廳、浴室、廚房等多種場景可供探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還有應粉絲呼聲實現的服裝，可自由搭配，打造只屬於兩人的專屬空間。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras_big/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新手也能安心上手</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坐著也能玩的簡易操作，VR 新手也能即刻沈浸其中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ HOS系統</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這個世界只有你與櫻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高度自由的觀看與觸碰，帶來甜蜜又帶點刺激的體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=360 height=203 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 2025 年 7 月 31 日 全球同步推出</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支援語言：日文 / 英文 / 中文（簡體・繁體）/ 韓文　※語音僅支援日語</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《VR女友》中，體驗前所未有的「零距離」戀愛！</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 零距離戀愛，即刻展開 -</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《VR女友》製作人傾力打造的全新作品──更有趣、更可愛！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在次世代 VR 戀愛模擬器 <strong>《VR女友》</strong>中，與女主角夕陽櫻在「幾乎鼻尖相觸」的距離甜蜜相伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即時全光源照明與全新著色器重現肌膚的透亮感與眼眸的光澤，戴上 VR 頭戴式顯示器，前所未有的臨場感瞬間包圍你。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >零距離真實感</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算近到鼻尖相碰也不失真，櫻輕聲呼吸的氣息都讓人沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >