o-of-us” space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras_big/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beginner-Friendly Controls</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple gameplay you can enjoy even while seated—perfect for VR newcomers who want to dive right into time with Sakura.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ HOS  System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you and Sakura exist in this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High freedom to look and touch creates a sweet yet slightly daring experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=360 height=203 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Worldwide Release Coming July 31 2025</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Languages supported: Japanese / English / Chinese (Simplified &amp; Traditional) / Korean  *Voice: Japanese only*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience an unparalleled “Zero-Distance” romance in “VR-Kanojo”!</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Zero-Distance Romance Begins -</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the producer of “VR Kanojo” comes a long-awaited new title—now even more fun and even cuter!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the next-generation VR romance sim <strong>“VR-Kanojo”</strong>, spend sweet time with the heroine Yuuhi Sakura at a nose-touching distance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time full lighting and a new shader recreate translucent skin and sparkling eyes, making her feel truly right in front of you. Slip on your VR headset and let an unprecedented sense of presence surround you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zero-Distance Realism</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even at nose-touching range, visual fidelity never breaks. Feel the immersion as Sakura softly breathes right before you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/b117e39a5043d7a688c374163ff35cd0.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/b117e39a5043d7a688c374163ff35cd0.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lover-Like Skinship</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold Sakura while she tidies a bookshelf, wash her in the bath, or share a heart-pounding kiss—enjoy unlimited flirting with intuitive <strong>“look &amp; touch”</strong> controls unique to VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fc8cbdddf16ec9b665ad6bc76d429968.mp4?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied Scenes &amp; Costumes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multiple locations such as the living room, bathroom, and kitchen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match fan-requested outfits to customize your private “just-the-two-of-us” space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras_big/1c877f2b462060fa5e4fd6cf0418b592.avif?t=1753923359 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beginner-Friendly Controls</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple gameplay you can enjoy even while seated—perfect for VR newcomers who want to dive right into time with Sakura.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ HOS  System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you and Sakura exist in this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High freedom to look and touch creates a sweet yet slightly daring experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.poster.avif?t=1753923359\" width=360 height=203 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/extras/fd739013e0ebe61746611c80b3137a67.webm?t=1753923359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Worldwide Release Coming July 31 2025</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Languages supported: Japanese / English / Chinese (Simplified &amp; Traditional) / Korean  *Voice: Japanese only*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience an unparalleled “Zero-Distance” romance in “VR-Kanojo”!</strong></p>", "short_description": "From the producer of &quot;VR Kanojo&quot; comes an even cuter VR romance sim. Spend zero-distance, nose-touching moments with heroine Sakura Yuuhi, brought to life by real-time full-lighting. Look-and-touch controls, multiple scenes and fan-picked outfits let you craft a private world. Beginner-friendly.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Korean<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/header.jpg?t=1753923359", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/a4e6651ffd697c3a1fc12aa078829f806078d585/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1753923359", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954880/a4e6651ffd697c3a1fc12aa078829f806078d585/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1753923359", "website": "https://vr-kanojo.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-9700 CPU @ 3.00GHz   3.00 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2070, 8 GB<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 6 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> Windows Compatible Audio Device<br></li><li><strong>VR Support:</strong> SteamVR</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</stro